<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>그룹 참여</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; padding: 2rem; }
    input { padding: 8px; width: 300px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>초대코드로 그룹 참여하기</h2>
